Gaijin 4Koma
[[Image:Gaijin4koma.jpg|thumb|right|180px|''"IT'S CALLED REACTION MEME, [[Fag|FAGGOT]][[Oneoneone|!1]]"'']]

'''"Gaijin 4Koma"''' (Japanese, 外人四こま, "4-frame foreigners") aka ''"reaction guys"'' aka ''"that meme with the four guys, you know the one"'' is a classic [[4chan]] [[meme]] [[stolen|appropriated]] from [[2chan]] typically consisting of a montage of four panels. Two of these panels depict four guys reacting to shit.

Needless to say, 4chan's /b/tards saw this as a prime candidate for [[Photoshop]]ping, and a meme was born.

==Origin==

[http://blogs.ign.com/Peer-IGN/2008/01/23/78041/ Read the fuckin IGN]

==Format==
Though it can often be expanded to more than four panels, the standard format of the meme is:
:'''Panel 1:''' Picture of [[Happy Negro]], [[Animu|Rei]], etc.
:'''Panel 2:''' Bored reaction.
:'''Panel 3:''' Picture of [[Cockmongler]].
:'''Panel 4:''' Cheering.

There is an alternative extension;
:'''Panel 1:''' Picture of [[Happy Negro]], [[Animu|Rei]], etc.
:'''Panel 2:''' Bored reaction.
:'''Panel 3:''' Picture of [[Cockmongler]].
:'''Panel 4:''' Cheering.
:'''Panel 5:''' Picture of any character.
:'''Panel 6:''' [[weegee|Bored reaction, but character's face is shooped over each gaijin's face.]]

Another extension;
:'''Panel 1:''' Picture of [[Happy Negro]], [[Animu|Rei]], etc.
:'''Panel 2:''' Bored reaction.
:'''Panel 3:''' Picture of [[Cockmongler]].
:'''Panel 4:''' Cheering.
:'''Panel 5:''' Picture of any character, usually someone particularly awesome.
:'''Panel 6:''' Cheering, with [[Za Warudo|colors inverted]], along with [[Lens flare|other suitable effects]].

==[[Controversy]]==
Mentioning the meme on [[b/|/b/]] will invariably result in a long, hilarious and bitter-fought [[flame war]] about what its true name is.

